serverSide.entities

Class ContestantsBenchClientProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • serverSide.entities.ContestantsBenchClientProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CoachCloning, ContestantCloning, RefereeCloning, java.lang.Runnable

    public class ContestantsBenchClientProxy
extends java.lang.Thread
implements RefereeCloning, CoachCloning, ContestantCloning
    Service provider agent for access to the Contestants Bench.

    Implementation of the client-server model type 2 (server replication). Communication is based on a communication channel under the TCP protocol.
